# --- Dependencies ---
# Ignore node_modules in every sub-service folder
**/node_modules
**/bower_components/
services/ai-service/node_modules/
services/user-service/node_modules/
# --- Environment & Secrets ---
# Crucial: Never commit your GEMINI_AI_API_KEY or other secrets
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local

# --- Build & Output ---
# If you use TypeScript or bundling (Vite/Webpack)
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.next/
**/.vercel/
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Debug & Logs ---
# Logs from Express or Docker
**/logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Docker ---
# Ignore local docker data or overrides if not shared
.docker-data/
docker-compose.override.yml

# --- Testing ---
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/

# --- IDE & OS ---
# System specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# --- Tooling ---
.eslintcache
.stylelintcache
.prettiercache